Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:43.76,top,,0,0,0,,喵西法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.98,top,,0,0,0,,三支牙刷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:57.25,top,,0,0,0,,欢迎莅临莫蒂堡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:37.66,top,,0,0,0,,加速器，需与搭档一同操作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:10.97,zh,,0,0,0,,是乌鸦人\N{\ren}It's the crow man!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.10,0:00:17.45,zh,,0,0,0,,先等一下\N{\ren}Give it a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:19.45,zh,,0,0,0,,他说不定是要投降\N{\ren}Maybe he's taking it out to surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.14,0:00:29.80,zh,,0,0,0,,他不是英雄，快逃\N{\ren}He's anti-heroic. Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:31.89,zh,,0,0,0,,我不懂\N{\ren}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:33.24,zh,,0,0,0,,他只是一个人而已\N{\ren}He's only one man!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:35.18,zh,,0,0,0,,我还有一千只乌鸦的力量\N{\ren}With the power of a thousand crows.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:41.10,zh,,0,0,0,,祝你好运\N{\ren}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.06,0:00:44.62,zh,,0,0,0,,乌鸦和猫头鹰一向是世仇\N{\ren}Crows and owls have always been at war,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:45.84,zh,,0,0,0,,但这跟你又有什么关系？\N{\ren}but why do you care?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:46.84,zh,,0,0,0,,有什么意义？\N{\ren}What's the point?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:49.23,zh,,0,0,0,,接招吧\N{\ren}Here's two.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:55.01,zh,,0,0,0,,-对，真酷 -莫蒂？\N{\ren}Ha-ha! Yeah. Cool. Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:56.88,zh,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\ren}Uh, h-hey, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:00:57.93,zh,,0,0,0,,真高兴能见到你\N{\ren}Good to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.23,0:01:01.10,zh,,0,0,0,,你好像还很着迷于\N{\ren}Y-You're, like, looking, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.15,0:01:02.67,zh,,0,0,0,,乌鸦\N{\ren}into crows...still.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:04.66,zh,,0,0,0,,两只乌鸦，这位是莫蒂\N{\ren}Oh, uh, two crows, you remember Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:06.27,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂，这是两只乌鸦\N{\ren}Morty, two crows.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.32,0:01:07.71,zh,,0,0,0,,很高兴能见到你\N{\ren}It's good to see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:09.10,zh,,0,0,0,,但你没事先说\N{\ren}but if you'd given me more of a heads up --
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.14,0:01:10.84,zh,,0,0,0,,我只是刚好来这附近，我不是…\N{\ren}Well, I-I was just in the neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:12.28,zh,,0,0,0,,因为乌鸦的战斗\N{\ren}I-It wasn't like --It's just that the battle for crows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.32,0:01:14.23,zh,,0,0,0,,永远不会停止\N{\ren}is kind of never-ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:15.18,zh,,0,0,0,,好\N{\ren}Huh. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:17.01,zh,,0,0,0,,那就有点没意义了，对吧？\N{\ren}A little pointless, then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.06,0:01:19.01,zh,,0,0,0,,我不是这个意思，太没礼貌了\N{\ren}That came out wrong, s-sounded judgy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:21.15,zh,,0,0,0,,-乌鸦马… -好吧，它们…\N{\ren}-Crowhorse. Crowhorse. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:23.28,zh,,0,0,0,,它们好像\N{\ren}Crowhorse. Crowhorse. Looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.32,0:01:25.92,zh,,0,0,0,,要带你去做什么事\N{\ren}looks like they're leading you to a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.97,0:01:27.14,zh,,0,0,0,,保重，莫蒂\N{\ren}Take care, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.19,0:01:28.27,zh,,0,0,0,,你也是\N{\ren}You -- You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:30.06,zh,,0,0,0,,我过得很好\N{\ren}I-I'm doing good, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.10,0:01:32.28,zh,,0,0,0,,我爸本来想喝你放在冰箱的酸奶\N{\ren}Oh, my dad was gonna eat that yogurt you left in the fridge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:33.02,zh,,0,0,0,,但我跟他说…\N{\ren}but I-I told him --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.92,0:02:18.01,zh,,0,0,0,,我在找\N{\ren}I'm looking for...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:20.15,zh,,0,0,0,,草稻人\N{\ren}Crow Scare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:22.80,zh,,0,0,0,,稻草人？邪恶的稻草人？\N{\ren}The scarecrow? The evil scarecrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:26.01,zh,,0,0,0,,拜托，最先供出他的人就能保命\N{\ren}Come on. Whoever gives him up first lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.05,0:02:28.10,zh,,0,0,0,,好吧，那我就多杀一个混帐\N{\ren}Fine, I can kill an extra asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:29.23,zh,,0,0,0,,这样运动量比较足够\N{\ren}Helps me get my steps in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.23,zh,,0,0,0,,-瑞克 -莫蒂？\N{\ren}Rick! Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:48.45,zh,,0,0,0,,木头？\N{\ren}Wood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.84,0:02:52.93,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂，你怎么变得像40岁？\N{\ren}Uh, Morty, why are you now like 40?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:54.36,zh,,0,0,0,,因为已经过这么久了，瑞克\N{\ren}Th-That's how long it's been, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:57.01,zh,,0,0,0,,那我们就可以一起喝一杯了\N{\ren}Oh, uh, I guess we can have a drink together, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:59.27,zh,,0,0,0,,有没有兰姆酒可乐？\N{\ren}Do you have a rum and Coke?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:00.36,zh,,0,0,0,,你才20岁吗？\N{\ren}What are you, 20?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:02.23,zh,,0,0,0,,别说笑了\N{\ren}Oh, bless your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.05,zh,,0,0,0,,时间过得真快，对吧？\N{\ren}Time be goin' by, don't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:05.79,zh,,0,0,0,,你没发现自己\N{\ren}That's your reaction to finding out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.84,0:03:07.27,zh,,0,0,0,,浪费了一辈子吗？\N{\ren}you wasted your entire life?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:08.23,zh,,0,0,0,,我觉得还好\N{\ren}I feel okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.27,0:03:09.67,zh,,0,0,0,,那我呢？\N{\ren}Well -- well, what about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.71,zh,,0,0,0,,我得请你们先\N{\ren}Whoa. Excuse us, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:13.71,zh,,0,0,0,,回避一下了\N{\ren}You don't wanna be here for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:15.01,zh,,0,0,0,,我以为只要给你一些空间\N{\ren}I thought if I gave you enough space,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.05,0:03:17.06,zh,,0,0,0,,你就会恢复正常\N{\ren}you'd outgrow this... phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:19.41,zh,,0,0,0,,这是你点的酒，做作鬼\N{\ren}Here's your drink, poser.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:21.89,zh,,0,0,0,,爸生病了，癌症晚期\N{\ren}Dad got sick, you know. Stage 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.93,0:03:23.28,zh,,0,0,0,,你一定会很开心\N{\ren}You would've loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:25.18,zh,,0,0,0,,桑美成为了护士，可以算是护士\N{\ren}Summer's a nurse -- well, pretty much a nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.23,0:03:27.27,zh,,0,0,0,,她嫁给了一个毒虫\N{\ren}She -- She married a junkie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:29.23,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克，快回家\N{\ren}Rick, come home,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.45,zh,,0,0,0,,我们还有点时间\N{\ren}while we still got a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:32.02,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂，我们之前的关系很不健康\N{\ren}Morty, what we had wasn't healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.83,zh,,0,0,0,,这就很健康吗？\N{\ren}And this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:35.23,zh,,0,0,0,,你跟乌鸦经历了无数场历险\N{\ren}Y-You've had a thousand adventures with these crows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:36.84,zh,,0,0,0,,你什么时候才要杀死大魔王？\N{\ren}When are you gonna kill their big bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:38.45,zh,,0,0,0,,首先，这种悬念\N{\ren}First off, the "will they/kill they"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:40.28,zh,,0,0,0,,对它们来说很重要\N{\ren}is everything to my guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:42.10,zh,,0,0,0,,而且去你的别想破坏我的幸福\N{\ren}And second, fuck you for trying to undermine my happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:44.10,zh,,0,0,0,,这可能是你最后一次见到我了\N{\ren}This may be the last time you ever lay eyes on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.14,0:03:45.71,zh,,0,0,0,,希望不是，莫蒂\N{\ren}I hope that's not true, Morty,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:47.45,zh,,0,0,0,,因为你状况很糟\N{\ren}because you look like s shit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:49.80,zh,,0,0,0,,我不想记得这样的你\N{\ren}and this is not how I wanna remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:05.10,zh,,0,0,0,,这两只乌鸦现在是我的了\N{\ren}Now that I have his two crows,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:08.01,zh,,0,0,0,,我总算能除掉乌鸦瑞克了\N{\ren}nothing will stop me from eliminating Crow Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.71,zh,,0,0,0,,不要帮他说话\N{\ren}Don't defend him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:11.49,zh,,0,0,0,,真不懂你们看上他哪一点\N{\ren}I don't even get what you see in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:13.02,zh,,0,0,0,,说得对\N{\ren}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:16.14,zh,,0,0,0,,我们应该好好享受在一起的时光\N{\ren}We should be enjoying the time we have together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:17.49,zh,,0,0,0,,乌鸦瑞克\N{\ren}Crow Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:19.01,zh,,0,0,0,,不要误会，我们…\N{\ren}Oh, I-I know what this must look like, but --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.06,0:04:21.23,zh,,0,0,0,,看来我的死对头草稻人\N{\ren}It looks like my arch nemesis, Crow Scare,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:23.50,zh,,0,0,0,,和我的搭档正在规划一起历险\N{\ren}and my sidekicks planning adventures together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:25.14,zh,,0,0,0,,你才不是受害者\N{\ren}You are hardly the victim here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:27.23,zh,,0,0,0,,早在你出现之前\N{\ren}I was adventuring with these two crows
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:29.27,zh,,0,0,0,,我就开始跟它们一起历险了\N{\ren}before you ever came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.58,zh,,0,0,0,,我是你们的备胎？\N{\ren}What do you mean, "using me as a rebound?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:39.36,zh,,0,0,0,,你们觉得我也把你们当备胎？\N{\ren}You feel like I was using you as a rebound, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:41.58,zh,,0,0,0,,靠，那就失去意义了\N{\ren}Well, shit, this lost all meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:43.02,zh,,0,0,0,,还不算太糟\N{\ren}I guess it could have been worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:44.57,zh,,0,0,0,,至少历险只是\N{\ren}At least adventuring was just a metaphor
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:46.79,zh,,0,0,0,,恋情的象征而已，所以这不算真正的分手\N{\ren}for romantic partnership, so it's not a real break-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.27,zh,,0,0,0,,不对\N{\ren}Speak for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.67,zh,,0,0,0,,我们也有亲密的肢体关系\N{\ren}We immensely enjoy each other's bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:52.28,zh,,0,0,0,,什么？不\N{\ren}What?! Ugh! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:53.67,zh,,0,0,0,,他好像想看证据\N{\ren}Sounds like the man's asking for proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:55.36,zh,,0,0,0,,就让他看看吧，两位\N{\ren}Let's show him, fellas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:57.06,zh,,0,0,0,,我没有要看证据\N{\ren}-I-I asked for zero proof! -Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:58.23,zh,,0,0,0,,坏鸟鸟\N{\ren}Zero proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:06.88,zh,,0,0,0,,我要给你自由意志\N{\ren}I'm giving you free will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:11.10,zh,,0,0,0,,向乌鸦马屈服吧\N{\ren}Submit to Crow Horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:19.23,zh,,0,0,0,,-瑞克？ -我回来了，朋友\N{\ren}-Rick? -Wubba lubba dub dub! I'm back, pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:20.93,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂，是谁来了？\N{\ren}Morty, who's at the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:22.63,zh,,0,0,0,,等等，你不是已经惨死了吗？\N{\ren}Wait a minute. I thought you died gruesomely?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:24.05,zh,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事？\N{\ren}W-what the hell's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.44,zh,,0,0,0,,其实…\N{\ren}See, uh, the -- the thing is, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:27.58,zh,,0,0,0,,你能把莫蒂变回14岁吗，爸？\N{\ren}Can you please make Morty 14 again, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:29.23,zh,,0,0,0,,这太荒谬了\N{\ren}This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:31.19,zh,,0,0,0,,好，听着，我可能用了老化药水\N{\ren}Okay, look, I-I may have used an aging serum
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:33.37,zh,,0,0,0,,稍微情绪勒索你了一下\N{\ren}to kind of emotionally blackmail you a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.01,zh,,0,0,0,,我猜到了，我完全能理解，莫蒂\N{\ren}I kind of figured, and I totally get it, Morty,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:36.88,zh,,0,0,0,,我受够那两只乌鸦了\N{\ren}I-I'm done with the two crows.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:39.06,zh,,0,0,0,,他们很黏人，我想跟你再试一次\N{\ren}Like, they were super clingy and I'm ready to make this work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.10,0:05:40.19,zh,,0,0,0,,我们就按下重置按钮吧\N{\ren}Let's just hit the reset button.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:42.19,zh,,0,0,0,,不，亲爱的，不要重置，好吗？\N{\ren}Well, no, honey, not a reset, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.23,0:05:44.92,zh,,0,0,0,,跟外公说，你值得他的尊重\N{\ren}Tell your grandpa that you're worthy of his respect
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:46.84,zh,,0,0,0,,你希望他之后换个方式对待你\N{\ren}and you want to be treated differently from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:48.01,zh,,0,0,0,,我不要\N{\ren}I refuse to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:49.41,zh,,0,0,0,,我很想跟他复合\N{\ren}I-I'm desperate to get back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:51.02,zh,,0,0,0,,-跟他爸一样 -别担心\N{\ren}-Just like his old man. -Don't worry, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:52.23,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂是变中年才会这样\N{\ren}That's just Morty's middle age talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:53.70,zh,,0,0,0,,等他还有更长的人生要过\N{\ren}He'll be less codependent once we get
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:55.27,zh,,0,0,0,,就不会这么黏人了\N{\ren}more of his life in front of him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:05:56.45,zh,,0,0,0,,我希望他继续40岁\N{\ren}Uh, I'd like him to stay 40
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:59.14,zh,,0,0,0,,这样他才能帮我朋友买摇头丸\N{\ren}so he can keep buying my friends molly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:00.23,zh,,0,0,0,,我宁愿放弃投票\N{\ren}I'd rather throw my vote away
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:02.15,zh,,0,0,0,,也不要支持有缺陷的系统\N{\ren}than use it to support a flawed system.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:04.10,zh,,0,0,0,,第一场历险能先把我变回来吗？\N{\ren}Can we make our first adventure fixing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:05.88,zh,,0,0,0,,-我一直在想草坪的事 -好吧\N{\ren}-I keep thinking about lawn care. -Okay, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:07.27,zh,,0,0,0,,谁卖这烂老化药水给你？\N{\ren}Who sold you this shitty aging serum?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.32,0:06:08.93,zh,,0,0,0,,-长什么样子？ -跟你一样\N{\ren}-What did he look like? -Just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.97,0:06:10.80,zh,,0,0,0,,-我是在大本营买的 -太棒了\N{\ren}-I-I got it from the Citadel. -Hot damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:12.89,zh,,0,0,0,,快来点大本营的情节吧\N{\ren}Hittin' the ground running with a Citadel episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:14.49,zh,,0,0,0,,再见了，各位废物\N{\ren}See ya later, masturbators.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:22.28,zh,,0,0,0,,嗨，我是大本营的新吉祥物小和\N{\ren}Hi! I'm Citadel's new mascot, Andy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:25.84,zh,,0,0,0,,因为这里有瑞克、和、莫蒂\N{\ren}because this place wouldn't be home without Ricks "Andy" Mortys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.10,zh,,0,0,0,,真蠢\N{\ren}Dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:28.23,zh,,0,0,0,,这里发生了什么事？\N{\ren}Ooh, what happened to this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:30.10,zh,,0,0,0,,这里现在有个莫蒂总统了\N{\ren}There's a Morty president now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:32.15,zh,,0,0,0,,真可爱，这里重建得很好\N{\ren}Aw, that's cute. They rebuilt. They made it nicer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:33.37,zh,,0,0,0,,这里变成格伦代尔了\N{\ren}They made it Glendale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:34.70,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，你脾气真暴躁\N{\ren}God damn, you are cantankerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:36.01,zh,,0,0,0,,我现在连拉屎都会痛\N{\ren}Even pooping hurts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:38.23,zh,,0,0,0,,是吗？这里会把你修好的\N{\ren}Yeah, well, this place is gonna fix you right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:40.15,zh,,0,0,0,,好，有个标准莫蒂\N{\ren}Okay, so, we've got a standard Morty
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:42.10,zh,,0,0,0,,被老化到40岁了吗？\N{\ren}that's been aged to...40?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:43.28,zh,,0,0,0,,可以逆转吗？\N{\ren}Can you reverse it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.32,0:06:44.88,zh,,0,0,0,,想成是骨头\N{\ren}Well, if you look at it like a bone,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.49,zh,,0,0,0,,我们可以把他的年龄\N{\ren}what we can do is break his age in two places,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:48.71,zh,,0,0,0,,断成三截，取出中间那段，再把头尾两段接起来\N{\ren}remove the middle, and graft its ends back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.41,zh,,0,0,0,,听起来好暴力\N{\ren}Th-that sounds really violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:52.15,zh,,0,0,0,,不是真正的骨头，莫蒂\N{\ren}It's not a literal bone, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:53.45,zh,,0,0,0,,好\N{\ren}Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:54.62,zh,,0,0,0,,但这过程也会\N{\ren}Ah, brace yourself, the process does also
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:56.05,zh,,0,0,0,,弄断全身的骨头\N{\ren}break every bone in your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.58,zh,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\ren}Wait! Aah! Ooh! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.62,0:07:00.54,zh,,0,0,0,,-我喜欢蜡笔 -女生好恶\N{\ren}-I like crayons. -Girls are gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:06.05,zh,,0,0,0,,我好像变回原样了\N{\ren}I-I think I feel like myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:07.14,zh,,0,0,0,,你看起来有点怪\N{\ren}Uh, you look a little weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.19,0:07:08.88,zh,,0,0,0,,全身都是粉红色，就像老鼠宝宝\N{\ren}Your skin's all pink like a baby mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:10.36,zh,,0,0,0,,-这是正常的吗？ -应该是\N{\ren}-I-Is that normal? -Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.10,zh,,0,0,0,,要存放或清除我们取出的26年\N{\ren}Uh, sign here for storage or disposal
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.15,0:07:13.19,zh,,0,0,0,,请在这里签名\N{\ren}of the 26 years we removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.57,zh,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\ren}Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:16.01,zh,,0,0,0,,我不要花钱存放那26年\N{\ren}I ain't payin' to store 26 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.01,zh,,0,0,0,,那你们就得带走\N{\ren}Well, then you're taking it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:20.80,zh,,0,0,0,,我快准备好抛弃原则了\N{\ren}I'm almost ready to sell out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:22.02,zh,,0,0,0,,好吧，清除要多少钱？\N{\ren}Alright, what's disposal cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.62,zh,,0,0,0,,发生了不公义的事\N{\ren}-Oh! -S-something unfair's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:27.23,zh,,0,0,0,,根本无法逃脱，无法逃脱\N{\ren}There's no escape. No escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.27,0:07:29.23,zh,,0,0,0,,我来帮你，这样不好看\N{\ren}Let me help you! This is not a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.23,zh,,0,0,0,,-天啊 -他们对我开了枪\N{\ren}-Oh, boy. -Hey! They -- they shot me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:34.01,zh,,0,0,0,,你对大本营体验造成很大的伤害\N{\ren}You are seriously hurting the Citadel experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.36,zh,,0,0,0,,-听我说 -把枪放下\N{\ren}-Listen to me! -Drop the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:36.79,zh,,0,0,0,,我们都即将面临死亡\N{\ren}Death is coming for us all,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:38.19,zh,,0,0,0,,大本营是大规模杀伤…\N{\ren}and the Citadel is a weapon of mass des--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:41.84,zh,,0,0,0,,你会被停职留薪\N{\ren}Woof. You're about to get suspended with pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:44.10,zh,,0,0,0,,走吧，莫蒂，这快变政治事件了\N{\ren}Come on, Morty, let's get outta here before this gets political.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:46.79,zh,,0,0,0,,我很有影响力吗？\N{\ren}Oh! Was I... influential?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:48.49,zh,,0,0,0,,对，你很有影响力\N{\ren}Yeah, y-you were influential.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:51.02,zh,,0,0,0,,你有七个博客\N{\ren}Y-You had like seven -- seven blogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:53.06,zh,,0,0,0,,赞\N{\ren}Tight. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.88,zh,,0,0,0,,太迟了\N{\ren}Ugh. Too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:56.18,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克C-137\N{\ren}Rick C-137,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:58.23,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂总统邀请你跟他共进晚餐\N{\ren}President Morty requests you join him for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:07:59.84,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，真的吗？\N{\ren}Whoa! S-Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:01.02,zh,,0,0,0,,我之前把这里摧毁了\N{\ren}You know I destroyed this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.80,zh,,0,0,0,,总统已经特赦你了，先生\N{\ren}You've been pardoned for that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:04.44,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克，我们去跟莫蒂总统吃饭\N{\ren}Rick! Let's have dinner with the Morty President.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.49,0:08:06.27,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂，我们该进行小历险才对\N{\ren}Morty, the idea was to get back to simple adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:07.88,zh,,0,0,0,,大本营都得按照正规剧情来\N{\ren}The Citadel runs on canon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:10.15,zh,,0,0,0,,好吧，看来状况真的\N{\ren}Okay. I guess things really are just going right back
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:11.19,zh,,0,0,0,,完全没变\N{\ren}to how they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:12.93,zh,,0,0,0,,好吧，我可以吃点东西\N{\ren}Fine. I could eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:15.01,zh,,0,0,0,,但他只要开始耍坏，我们就走人\N{\ren}But the second he reveals he's evil, we're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.62,0:08:20.67,zh,,0,0,0,,这其实还蛮好吃的\N{\ren}I dunno. It tastes... pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:22.50,zh,,0,0,0,,好，你有中毒感再告诉我\N{\ren}Okay, let me know if you start feeling poisony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.05,zh,,0,0,0,,很高兴能跟你合体\N{\ren}Good to have you back, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:28.19,zh,,0,0,0,,抱歉，我迟到了，有好多事要忙\N{\ren}Sorry I'm late. Never really ends around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:29.62,zh,,0,0,0,,你看\N{\ren}Look at this, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.67,0:08:31.10,zh,,0,0,0,,真的有莫蒂选上总统了\N{\ren}They really did make a you the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:32.23,zh,,0,0,0,,我每天都很讨厌选我的人\N{\ren}And I hate 'em every day for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.49,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，瑞克C-137\N{\ren}But wow! Rick C-137.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:36.88,zh,,0,0,0,,你是需要特别排开行程见的贵宾\N{\ren}Now, that's a guy to move your schedule around for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:38.88,zh,,0,0,0,,希望你不会再来把这里炸烂\N{\ren}Not -- Not here to blow the place up again, I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:40.93,zh,,0,0,0,,除非你想把我留下来\N{\ren}Ha! Not unless you try to keep me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:42.28,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，我想都不敢想\N{\ren}Ha-ha, geez. Wouldn't dream of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:43.83,zh,,0,0,0,,但你能来真是太好了\N{\ren}But it's amazing you dropped by
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.88,0:08:45.79,zh,,0,0,0,,因为我本来想找你\N{\ren}because I was eventually gonna hunt you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:47.58,zh,,0,0,0,,他要耍坏了，来吧\N{\ren}There's the reveal. Let's dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:49.23,zh,,0,0,0,,-真是的 -瑞克，别这样\N{\ren}-Ha! Geez. -Rick, come on, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:51.36,zh,,0,0,0,,他都选上总统了，是瑞克和莫蒂选的\N{\ren}The guy got elected president by Ricks and Mortys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:53.44,zh,,0,0,0,,-他人很好 -每个政客人都很好\N{\ren}-He's being really nice. -All politicians are nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.05,zh,,0,0,0,,他脾气还真暴躁，对吧？\N{\ren}He's a hot bag of peanuts, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:56.71,zh,,0,0,0,,我们经历了很多事\N{\ren}We've been through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:58.67,zh,,0,0,0,,他不喜欢…连续剧情\N{\ren}A-And he does not like --Serialized drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.80,zh,,0,0,0,,好，只要走单集剧情就好\N{\ren}Right, no drama. Keep it episodic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.84,0:09:02.10,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克从不留恋过去\N{\ren}Ricks never look back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:03.88,zh,,0,0,0,,这对传奇人物来说太可惜了\N{\ren}Waste of a legend in his case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.92,0:09:05.84,zh,,0,0,0,,-你知道这里算是他建立的吗？ -等等，什么？\N{\ren}-You know he practically built this place? -Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:08.06,zh,,0,0,0,,你现在经营得很好，对吧？\N{\ren}And now you're running it squeaky clean, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:09.01,zh,,0,0,0,,才会有畸形莫蒂\N{\ren}That's why you got deformed Mortys
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:10.23,zh,,0,0,0,,从下水道冒出来\N{\ren}coming up through the sewer lines
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:12.10,zh,,0,0,0,,说着关于希望和改变的事？\N{\ren}talking about hope and change?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:14.05,zh,,0,0,0,,-有道理 -回嘴回得好，瑞克\N{\ren}-Fair enough. -Good clapback, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.18,zh,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事，总统？\N{\ren}What's the deal with that, Mister P?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:16.84,zh,,0,0,0,,我正在执行某项计划\N{\ren}I got a little project going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.14,zh,,0,0,0,,需要劳力\N{\ren}Required some hands-on labor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:20.01,zh,,0,0,0,,告诉我该如何降低中心有限曲线\N{\ren}It would require less if you were willing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.19,zh,,0,0,0,,我就不需要\N{\ren}to tell me how one might
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.23,0:09:23.06,zh,,0,0,0,,那么多人力了\N{\ren}bring down the Central Finite Curve.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:24.44,zh,,0,0,0,,好，我们该走了，莫蒂\N{\ren}Alright, time to go, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:25.66,zh,,0,0,0,,我想知道他在讲什么\N{\ren}I want to know what he's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:26.92,zh,,0,0,0,,对啊，你们都大老远来了\N{\ren}Yeah, you've come all this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:28.23,zh,,0,0,0,,再给我十秒，好吗？\N{\ren}Can you give me 10 more seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:30.10,zh,,0,0,0,,那你现在只剩六秒了\N{\ren}Literally 10? Because now it would be 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:31.23,zh,,0,0,0,,没关系\N{\ren}Oh, I'm fine with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:32.89,zh,,0,0,0,,倒数二\N{\ren}Make it 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:34.62,zh,,0,0,0,,一…\N{\ren}One.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:36.23,zh,,0,0,0,,你如果告诉我会很有帮助\N{\ren}Like I said, would have been a big help for you to tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:38.36,zh,,0,0,0,,但我需要的情报应该都到手了\N{\ren}but I should have everything I need from you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:40.01,zh,,0,0,0,,我确认一下\N{\ren}Let me just make sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:42.15,zh,,0,0,0,,吃前菜的时间无法扫描整个大脑\N{\ren}You can't scan an entire brain over appetizers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:45.71,zh,,0,0,0,,你大部分大脑的内容都在很久之前就扫描过了\N{\ren}Oh, most of yours got scanned a longtime ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:47.01,zh,,0,0,0,,你可能不记得了\N{\ren}You probably don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.27,zh,,0,0,0,,回去看第一季第九集，笨蛋\N{\ren}Check out season 1, episode 9, Rick Heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:51.28,zh,,0,0,0,,精益求精\N{\ren}Excel sior!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.06,zh,,0,0,0,,-邪恶瑞克 -我们教训了他\N{\ren}-Evil Rick. -We kicked his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:54.57,zh,,0,0,0,,邪恶瑞克，我喜欢\N{\ren}"Evil Rick." I love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:56.05,zh,,0,0,0,,他是全宇宙最聪明的人\N{\ren}Smartest man in the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:58.71,zh,,0,0,0,,又很自大，很好操控\N{\ren}with an ego so big you can just grab it like a joystick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.36,zh,,0,0,0,,看起来很完整\N{\ren}Looks complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:01.80,zh,,0,0,0,,我还担心要杀光大本营里的瑞克\N{\ren}I was afraid I'd have to kill every Rick
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:03.10,zh,,0,0,0,,才能得到我要的东西\N{\ren}on the Citadel to get what I needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:05.14,zh,,0,0,0,,王八蛋，我还帮你担保了\N{\ren}You asshole! I vouched for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.18,0:10:07.14,zh,,0,0,0,,他会来都是因为我说想来\N{\ren}He only came here because I asked him to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:08.27,zh,,0,0,0,,对不起，瑞克\N{\ren}I'm sorry, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:09.80,zh,,0,0,0,,道歉跟给我一把螺丝刀\N{\ren}That apology and a screwdriver in my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:11.02,zh,,0,0,0,,我比较需要螺丝刀\N{\ren}would be worth a screwdriver.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:12.67,zh,,0,0,0,,我真讨厌你们这些没原则的莫蒂\N{\ren}You sellout Mortys kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.23,zh,,0,0,0,,你们比你们崇拜的瑞克更讨人厌\N{\ren}I'd hate you more than the Ricks you worship
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:15.44,zh,,0,0,0,,但这并没有意义\N{\ren}if there was any point.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:16.84,zh,,0,0,0,,你也是情不自禁\N{\ren}But you can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.88,0:10:18.01,zh,,0,0,0,,你天生就这样\N{\ren}You were bred for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:19.49,zh,,0,0,0,,你想看吗？\N{\ren}Wanna see?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:24.18,zh,,0,0,0,,你知道离群瑞克利用了莫蒂\N{\ren}You already know Rogue Ricks used Mortys
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.23,0:10:26.58,zh,,0,0,0,,让大本营找不到他们\N{\ren}to hide themselves from the Citadel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:28.06,zh,,0,0,0,,但你或许不知道这计谋太成功了\N{\ren}But you might not know it worked so well
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.67,zh,,0,0,0,,大本营都变成了\N{\ren}that the Citadel became its own
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:31.15,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂市场\N{\ren}Morty Market.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.02,zh,,0,0,0,,你也不知道他们为了提高供给量\N{\ren}And I'm sure you don't know how far they've gone
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:35.01,zh,,0,0,0,,会做到什么地步\N{\ren}to help supply meet demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:36.66,zh,,0,0,0,,对，瑞克也可以到无限个宇宙去\N{\ren}Sure, Ricks could scour infinity
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:38.19,zh,,0,0,0,,寻找自然产生的孙子\N{\ren}for naturally occurring grandsons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:39.58,zh,,0,0,0,,但何必呢？\N{\ren}But why bother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:41.10,zh,,0,0,0,,那样太麻烦了\N{\ren}So much work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:43.24,zh,,0,0,0,,还得承认自己的需要\N{\ren}Such an admission of need.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:45.84,zh,,0,0,0,,我们的外公并没有无限个版本\N{\ren}There aren't infinite versions of our grandfather, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:48.45,zh,,0,0,0,,他只是同一个糟老头的无限副本\N{\ren}He's an infinite smear of one shitty old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.49,0:10:50.28,zh,,0,0,0,,他永远离不开我们\N{\ren}And he's attached to us infinitely
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:53.06,zh,,0,0,0,,因为他很软弱，我们又善于原谅\N{\ren}through his weakness and our forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:55.88,zh,,0,0,0,,所以我们才会跟他在一起\N{\ren}This is why we're with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:57.49,zh,,0,0,0,,所以我们才会活着\N{\ren}This is why we're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.19,0:11:03.10,zh,,0,0,0,,搞什么？\N{\ren}What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.15,0:11:04.23,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克，快说这不是事实\N{\ren}Rick, say this isn't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:06.01,zh,,0,0,0,,-这不全是事实 -骗子\N{\ren}-It isn't the whole truth. -Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:08.19,zh,,0,0,0,,-说来话长 -我现在很闲\N{\ren}-It's complicated! -I'm not busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.23,0:11:10.01,zh,,0,0,0,,好，莫蒂，我不是说过比起道歉\N{\ren}Okay, Morty, remember when I said all I need
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:12.06,zh,,0,0,0,,我比较需要螺丝刀吗？\N{\ren}was your apology and a screwdriver in my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:14.66,zh,,0,0,0,,我忘了我手里确实有把螺丝刀\N{\ren}Well, I forgot I literally have a screwdriver in my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:17.10,zh,,0,0,0,,废话，我简直就是神探加杰特\N{\ren}I mean, duh-doy. I'm basically Inspector Gadget.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.75,0:11:21.89,zh,,0,0,0,,没关系，放他走吧\N{\ren}It's okay. He's free to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:25.18,zh,,0,0,0,,他是最瑞克的瑞克，我们再也不会见到他了\N{\ren}He's the Rickest Rick. We'll never see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:28.71,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂，你来买老化药水时\N{\ren}Morty, when you came here for that serum,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:30.19,zh,,0,0,0,,有没有补过传送液？\N{\ren}did you refill this gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.23,0:11:31.49,zh,,0,0,0,,有\N{\ren}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.54,0:11:34.27,zh,,0,0,0,,靠\N{\ren}Oh. Ooh! Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:36.71,zh,,0,0,0,,能破解我的传送枪的只有一个人\N{\ren}I only know one man that ever hacked my portal gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:38.58,zh,,0,0,0,,就是邪恶的你\N{\ren}and it turned out it was evil you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:40.71,zh,,0,0,0,,真棒，他全都搞懂了\N{\ren}Yay! He's all caught up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:43.66,zh,,0,0,0,,等等，先住手…\N{\ren}Wait. Hold it. Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:48.27,zh,,0,0,0,,-那是谁？ -大胃王该登场了，躲起来\N{\ren}-Who -- Who's that? -Time for Big Boy. Duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.97,0:11:52.15,zh,,0,0,0,,他很享受吗？\N{\ren}Does he like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:53.40,zh,,0,0,0,,这象征着资本主义，莫蒂\N{\ren}It's a metaphor for capitalism, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:55.23,zh,,0,0,0,,你觉得呢？\N{\ren}What do you think?
;Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:13.70,zh,,0,0,0,,\ren}Yoink!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:16.40,zh,,0,0,0,,你是无法逃避过去的，瑞克\N{\ren}You can't outrun your past, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:19.06,zh,,0,0,0,,你以为我会突然卸除力场吗？\N{\ren}Did you think my force field would be down the second time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:21.49,zh,,0,0,0,,我是在对你的言论表达不满\N{\ren}I was expressing disapproval of your dialogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.54,0:12:23.40,zh,,0,0,0,,你就尽管不满吧\N{\ren}Disapprove all you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:26.45,zh,,0,0,0,,到了今晚，言论品质就不重要了\N{\ren}Tonight, the quality of dialogue stops mattering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:29.23,zh,,0,0,0,,到了今晚，我就能如愿\N{\ren}Tonight, I do that thing I want to do
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:30.88,zh,,0,0,0,,降低曲线\N{\ren}with the curve thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:37.10,zh,,0,0,0,,谁都别离开，全都留下来…\N{\ren}Nobody leave. Everybody stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.14,0:12:38.36,zh,,0,0,0,,谁都别离开，全都留下来\N{\ren}Nobody leave. Everybody stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:48.01,zh,,0,0,0,,谁都别离开，全都留下来\N{\ren}Nobody leave. Everybody stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.71,zh,,0,0,0,,在这种动荡时机\N{\ren}In uncertain times like these,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.75,0:12:51.80,zh,,0,0,0,,我有重要的话要说：＂去撞墙，干你娘＂\N{\ren}I think it's important for me to say, eat shit, fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:53.44,zh,,0,0,0,,每句话都是药厂花钱请我讲的\N{\ren}The drug companies paid for me to say every word.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:54.88,zh,,0,0,0,,我有很多钱\N{\ren}I have millions of dollars,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:56.45,zh,,0,0,0,,我不在乎你们…\N{\ren}and I don't care if you live -- oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:12:58.62,zh,,0,0,0,,不，干，不\N{\ren}Oh, fuck! No! Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:00.58,zh,,0,0,0,,我觉得处方药很棒\N{\ren}And I'd just like to say that prescription drugs are great,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:02.80,zh,,0,0,0,,你们应该马上去买\N{\ren}and you should buy them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:04.27,zh,,0,0,0,,怎么回事，瑞克？\N{\ren}What's happening, Rick?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:05.62,zh,,0,0,0,,他对大本营的传送液都动了手脚\N{\ren}He hacked the entire city's portal supply.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.58,zh,,0,0,0,,走吧，我们或许还有办法能离开\N{\ren}Come on, there still might be one way out of here --
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:08.71,zh,,0,0,0,,从底下离开\N{\ren}out the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.58,zh,,0,0,0,,他想从你的大脑里找到什么？\N{\ren}What do you think he needed from your brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:19.27,zh,,0,0,0,,应该是大本营的维度驱动设计图\N{\ren}I assume schematics for the Citadel's dimensional drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:20.67,zh,,0,0,0,,他若想破坏曲线\N{\ren}If he's gonna use it to blow the curve,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:22.10,zh,,0,0,0,,我们最好快逃\N{\ren}we do notwant to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:23.02,zh,,0,0,0,,中心有限曲线是什么？\N{\ren}What is the Central Finite Curve?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:24.84,zh,,0,0,0,,我们先活下来，我再开放提问\N{\ren}Q&A after our survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:27.14,zh,,0,0,0,,希望能从源头取得未污染传送液\N{\ren}Hopefully we can snag some untainted fluid at the source
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:29.62,zh,,0,0,0,,然后离开这里\N{\ren}and get the fuck out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:31.19,zh,,0,0,0,,可能没办法了\N{\ren}Or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:36.05,zh,,0,0,0,,我以为我的资本主义比喻很强了\N{\ren}Wow. I thought mycapitalism metaphor was on the nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.14,0:13:39.67,zh,,0,0,0,,你有帮忙建造大本营吗？\N{\ren}So did you help build the Citadel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.02,zh,,0,0,0,,你是不是什么事都对我说谎？\N{\ren}Do you just lie to me about everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:42.89,zh,,0,0,0,,我们能先专心穿越地洞基地吗？\N{\ren}Can't we just sneak through the cave base?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:45.05,zh,,0,0,0,,我们重新开始了，莫蒂，我们要继续进行简单的历险\N{\ren}We turned a new leaf, Morty. We're back to simple adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:47.10,zh,,0,0,0,,你要对我说实话才算重新开始\N{\ren}It's not a new leaf until you tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:48.71,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂，我们真的没时间\N{\ren}Morty, we really don't have time for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:50.58,zh,,0,0,0,,-这里要爆炸了 -不，我不信任你\N{\ren}-The whole place is gonna blow. -No, I-I don't trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:52.28,zh,,0,0,0,,你如果不直接回答我\N{\ren}I-I don't want to do this anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:53.70,zh,,0,0,0,,我就不想继续跟你探险了\N{\ren}if I'm not gonna get straight answers from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:55.23,zh,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\ren}God damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:56.14,zh,,0,0,0,,这是我大脑的内容，莫蒂\N{\ren}Here's my fucking downloaded brain, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:57.79,zh,,0,0,0,,你想看精彩情节吗？\N{\ren}You want to jump the shark?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:13:59.23,zh,,0,0,0,,你想知道我愚蠢的可怜故事吗？\N{\ren}You want to know my stupid crybaby backstory?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:01.71,zh,,0,0,0,,那就随你便，不是现在\N{\ren}Knock yourself out. Not -- not now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:23.05,zh,,0,0,0,,-做得好，莫蒂 -这样如何？\N{\ren}-Boo ya, Rick. -Nice one, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:26.58,zh,,0,0,0,,你太太死了？\N{\ren}Whoa. Dead wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:28.45,zh,,0,0,0,,对，大家现在可以闭嘴了\N{\ren}Yes, now everyone can shut up about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:31.89,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，瑞克，我看过之后，心里好受多了\N{\ren}Wow, Rick, I feel a lot better having seen all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:33.14,zh,,0,0,0,,当然是这样啦\N{\ren}Of course that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:36.23,zh,,0,0,0,,在他们眼中，自己才是居于劣势\N{\ren}In their minds, they're the underdogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:38.45,zh,,0,0,0,,所以他们才能合理化这一切\N{\ren}And that's how they justify this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:42.02,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂，我不能\N{\ren}Morty, I'm not responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:43.18,zh,,0,0,0,,为所有烂瑞克负责\N{\ren}for every fucked-up Rick out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:44.44,zh,,0,0,0,,每个瑞克都是这样说\N{\ren}They literally all say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.49,0:16:45.71,zh,,0,0,0,,他们都有一样的借口\N{\ren}They all have that excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:47.10,zh,,0,0,0,,这是他们的本质\N{\ren}It's part of their system.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:48.23,zh,,0,0,0,,他们都不用负责任\N{\ren}None of them have to be responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:50.06,zh,,0,0,0,,他们都是自己的受害者\N{\ren}They're all victims of themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:52.80,zh,,0,0,0,,当天才好辛苦，你为什么不能直接死掉？\N{\ren}Oh, it's so hard to be a genius. Couldn't you just die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:53.88,zh,,0,0,0,,你打算怎么做？\N{\ren}Well, what are you doing about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:55.44,zh,,0,0,0,,我什么都不做，我要走了\N{\ren}Jack shit. I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.45,zh,,0,0,0,,你知道中心有限曲线是什么吗？\N{\ren}Do you know what the Central Finite Curve is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.49,0:16:59.14,zh,,0,0,0,,他们沿着无限建了一道墙\N{\ren}They built a wall around infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:01.15,zh,,0,0,0,,他们把所有无限宇宙\N{\ren}They separated all the infinite universes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:04.57,zh,,0,0,0,,跟自己是最聪明的人的无限宇宙分开\N{\ren}from all the infinite universes where he's the smartest man in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.05,zh,,0,0,0,,每一版的我们都在\N{\ren}Every version of us has spent every version
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:11.02,zh,,0,0,0,,为无限宝宝建造的无限摇篮里过了一辈子\N{\ren}of all of our lives in one infinite crib built around an infinite fucking baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:12.06,zh,,0,0,0,,我要离开\N{\ren}And I'm leaving it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.49,zh,,0,0,0,,所以才会被视为邪恶\N{\ren}That's what makes me evil --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.05,zh,,0,0,0,,因为我受够他了\N{\ren}being sick of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:17.71,zh,,0,0,0,,你如果受够他，就会被视为邪恶\N{\ren}If you've ever been sick of him, you've been evil, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:21.36,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克，你真的是为了我才离开乌鸦的吗？\N{\ren}Rick, did you really leave the crows for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:24.92,zh,,0,0,0,,还是你被他们甩了才回来？\N{\ren}Or did you come back because they dumped you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:28.14,zh,,0,0,0,,这就对了，你也变成邪恶莫蒂了\N{\ren}There you go, kid. Now you're Evil Morty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:29.84,zh,,0,0,0,,我们在曲线的这一边\N{\ren}Sooner or later we all are,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.88,0:17:31.71,zh,,0,0,0,,迟早都会变邪恶莫蒂\N{\ren}on this side of the curve.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:47.49,zh,,0,0,0,,别担心，莫蒂，我们还有\N{\ren}Don't worry, Morty. We still got a way out
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:49.41,zh,,0,0,0,,他们没想到的离开方式——凤凰行动\N{\ren}they never thought of -- Operation Phoenix.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.45,0:17:51.02,zh,,0,0,0,,不就是求死吗？\N{\ren}Doesn't that still mean, like, death?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.06,0:17:52.63,zh,,0,0,0,,对，但糗的是他们\N{\ren}Sure, but the joke's on them,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:54.27,zh,,0,0,0,,我们发现了离开这星球的方式\N{\ren}'cause we just found a backdoor to getting off this rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:58.36,zh,,0,0,0,,改变路线\N{\ren}REROUTED. REROUTED.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.40,0:18:01.10,zh,,0,0,0,,改变路线…\N{\ren}Rerouted. Rerouted. Rerouted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:05.62,zh,,0,0,0,,改变路线…\N{\ren}Rerouted. Rerouted. Rerouted.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:09.58,zh,,0,0,0,,他妈的老天爷啊\N{\ren}Oh, my fucking God!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:11.28,zh,,0,0,0,,快，莫蒂，我们得走了\N{\ren}Come on, Morty. We gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:15.14,zh,,0,0,0,,你可以跟我走\N{\ren}You can come if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:16.84,zh,,0,0,0,,不想走就别怪我\N{\ren}Don't blame me if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.88,0:18:18.84,zh,,0,0,0,,在我看来，莫蒂\N{\ren}Ugh! From where I sit, Morty,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:20.06,zh,,0,0,0,,这是你最好的选择\N{\ren}that's the best deal on the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:23.88,zh,,0,0,0,,我其实没有计划\N{\ren}I-I don't have a real plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.53,0:18:28.84,zh,,0,0,0,,谢了，很高兴你无视了我的建议\N{\ren}Thanks, pal. I-I'm glad you ignored my advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:30.71,zh,,0,0,0,,这样也好，我骗了你\N{\ren}It's just as well. I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:32.23,zh,,0,0,0,,第二个座位是马桶\N{\ren}That second seat's a toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.28,0:18:34.01,zh,,0,0,0,,真是混蛋\N{\ren}Oh. Super dick move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:35.66,zh,,0,0,0,,但你坦承说谎还蛮酷的\N{\ren}But weirdly kind of cool to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:37.45,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，你们还真善于原谅\N{\ren}Geez, you guys really are bred for forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.49,0:18:39.27,zh,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\ren}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:56.79,zh,,0,0,0,,跟大本营道别吧，各位\N{\ren}Say goodbye to the Citadel, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.19,0:20:53.44,zh,,0,0,0,,邪恶莫蒂\N{\ren}Ooowee! Evil Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.49,0:20:55.23,zh,,0,0,0,,好酷的计谋\N{\ren}That was quite a scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:57.71,zh,,0,0,0,,我很好奇有没有邪恶的我\N{\ren}Makes me wonder if there's an evil me out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:21:00.06,zh,,0,0,0,,但仔细看看我的人生\N{\ren}But I guess sometimes I look at my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.10,0:21:02.92,zh,,0,0,0,,我可能根本就不需要邪恶的我\N{\ren}and I may not even need him, 'cause, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:05.40,zh,,0,0,0,,因为我自己就能把事情搞砸了\N{\ren}guess I've made a pretty big mess of things myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:09.01,zh,,0,0,0,,我没找回大学的工作\N{\ren}Never got my job at the university back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:11.45,zh,,0,0,0,,记得吗？瑞克逼我练空手道\N{\ren}Remember that? Rick made me do karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:13.09,zh,,0,0,0,,蛮好笑的\N{\ren}It -- It was kinda funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:15.05,zh,,0,0,0,,但在那之后，一切就都走下坡了\N{\ren}But I guess things went downhill from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:17.45,zh,,0,0,0,,我也开始跟艾咪疏远\N{\ren}Started isolating myself from Amy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:19.84,zh,,0,0,0,,我之前什么心事都会跟她说\N{\ren}Used to tell her everything I was feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:21.41,zh,,0,0,0,,但我后来就不说了\N{\ren}but then I guess I stopped,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:23.88,zh,,0,0,0,,因为我希望她能爱她心目中的我\N{\ren}'cause I wanted her to love who she thought I was,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:26.23,zh,,0,0,0,,而不是我即将变成的那个样子\N{\ren}not who I felt myself becoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.27,0:21:28.62,zh,,0,0,0,,你有想过我们心爱的人如果看清我们真正的样子\N{\ren}Ever think about how horrified the people we love would be
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.67,0:21:30.67,zh,,0,0,0,,他们会有多惊慌吗？\N{\ren}if they found out who we truly are?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.71,0:21:34.66,zh,,0,0,0,,所以我们每天越讲越多谎言\N{\ren}So we just dig ourselves deeper into our lies every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:38.14,zh,,0,0,0,,最后还是伤害了少数有勇气爱我们的人\N{\ren}ultimately hurting the only people brave enough to love us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:39.84,zh,,0,0,0,,真希望我没这么做\N{\ren}Wish I didn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:42.10,zh,,0,0,0,,真希望我也有勇气爱他们\N{\ren}Wish I was brave enough to love them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:44.66,zh,,0,0,0,,我也不知道，或许你该试试看\N{\ren}I don't know. Maybe you should try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.70,0:21:46.84,zh,,0,0,0,,时间并没有我们想像中的那么多\N{\ren}We don't have as much time as we think.